## Architecture

Clean / hexagonal architecture with strict Dependency Rule:
- `core/` → Pure domain (entities, enums, interfaces) — ZERO external deps
- `application/` → Use cases, services, DTOs — imports from core only
- `adapters/` → DB repos, cache, HTTP clients — implements core interfaces
- `ports/` → API routes, CLI — FastAPI/Click allowed
- `config/` → Settings, DI container
- `utils/` → Shared helpers — stdlib + third-party only

Dependency direction: `adapters → ports → application → core`

## Conventions

- Python: type hints everywhere, Google-style docstrings, keyword-only args (`*`),
  `from __future__ import annotations`, no `Any` type, structured logging with structlog
- TypeScript: strict mode, no `any`, Tailwind CSS v4
- Shell: `.zsh` extension, `emulate -L zsh`, `setopt ERR_EXIT PIPE_FAIL`
- Constants: plain `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE` (no `Final` annotation)
- Enums: `StrEnum` + `@unique` + `auto()`

