## Behavior

- Always run `task lint` after editing Python files
- Always run `task registry:check` after changing naming_registry.json
- Never use `print()` — use structured logging
- Never hardcode field/column names — use registry constants
- Never use raw SQL — use SQLAlchemy ORM
